          "date": "2012-09-04 02:49:05.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1512 oi: more test case for reusing idle OI blocks",
        "message": "LU-1512 oi: more test case for reusing idle OI blocks\n\nThe recycled empty OI blocks should be recorded on divice and be\nre-loaded after the device remount. Then they can be reused when\nneeds new OI blocks.\n\nNeed not check iam_container::ic_idle_failed in iam_new_node().\n\nClear iam_frame::at_shifted when iam_path_release().\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I1a705ee5fda4fd612c488dbe5b9ab06e4b1af9ec\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
